  I hope someone will have an answer, as i hate having to wake up at 7 just because of the sound of dogs barking, curling dogs in my own yard as well, and geez, the smell. I had to move a lot this year, due to a rustling dog on the roof. Some guy told "You should sew him in and click your fingers, he'll follow you home". I can't! I got a sore throat because of it. I just want something to keep the dog in in my flat. I live in a student house, and saying "i have a dog" mostly means you got 5$ at the end of the month. They keep my flat/couch clean and make no problems and i'm alright with that.
